        "id": "ambush",
        "name": "Ambush",
        "type": "skill",
        "rulesText": "1. Use when enemy ends Move within 4 squares and you are in cover. Make a Ranged Attack against them. You may Dash before or after.\n2. Use when enemy ends Move within 4 squares and you are in cover. Make a Move and then an Attack against them. You may Dash once before or after either action.\n3. Use when enemy ends Move within 4 squares and you are in cover. Make a Move, an Attack, and a Move. You may Dash once before or after any of these actions.",
        "tags": [
          "marksman",
          "profession"
        ],
        "source": {
