        "name": "Bullseye",
        "type": "skill",
        "rulesText": "1. Make short-range Ranged Attack. Do not roll. Scores 1 hit, ignoring cover.\n2. Make medium-range Ranged Attack. Do not roll. Scores 1 hit, ignoring cover and physical armour.\n3. Make medium-range Ranged Attack. Do not roll. Scores 2 hits, ignoring cover and physical armour.",
        "tags": [
          "marksman",
          "profession"
        ],
        "source": {
