        "id": "countershot",
        "name": "Countershot",
        "type": "skill",
        "rulesText": "1. Use when targeted with ranged attack/spell, before resolving. Make Ranged Attack/cast spell against attacker.\n2. Use at any time after target enemy takes first action each round. Make Ranged Attack/cast spell against target.\n3. Use any time. Make Ranged Attack/cast spell against enemy with +1 die, then Move.",
        "tags": [
          "marksman",
          "profession"
        ],
        "source": {
          "name": "reference-marksman.pdf",
          "url": "imports/maladum-cards/reference-marksman.pdf"
