        "name": "Intimidating",
        "type": "skill",
        "rulesText": "1. Reaction: Use when enemy in LoS activates. Choose their target.\n2. Reaction: Use when enemy enters LoS or starts turn in LoS. Their turn ends and they are Stunned. Passive: As an effortless action, take an action with friend in short range. Then become Fatigued.\n3. All enemies up to this character's rank within short range and LoS are Stunned and Terrified. Passive: Gain Terrifying.",
        "tags": [
          "magus",
