      {
        "id": "brutal-assault",
        "name": "Brutal Assault",
        "type": "skill",
        "rulesText": "1. Make a Melee Attack using +1 dice. Lay target prone.\n2. Choose character engaged with you up to your size. Move them to any square in short range and LoS with no AoO. They suffer attack with +1 dice, adding 1 die if they hit a wall or terrain piece. Lay them prone. If they hit a character, it suffers the same attack. Passive: Ignore Cumbersome for melee weapons.\n3. Make up to three Melee Attacks with +1 dice. Lay target prone. Then Move.",
        "tags": [
