        "id": "impervious",
        "name": "Impervious",
        "type": "skill",
        "rulesText": "1. Reaction: Use when you would suffer a status counter. Discard it.\n2. Gain +2 armour until end of round.\n3. Restore 1 Health (even above starting level). Discard any status counters. You may ignore all damage, resist all spells, and discard all status counters suffered until end of round.",
