      },
      {
        "id": "camouflage",
        "name": "Camouflage",
        "type": "skill",
        "rulesText": "1. While in contact with a wall you cannot be targeted until end of round. Enemies can move through adjacent squares without stopping or suffering AoO but cannot end a Move in contact with you. You do not block LoS.\n2. Make a Move or Ranged Attack. Then, while in contact with any terrain you cannot be targeted until end of round, as above.\n3. While not in contact with an enemy you cannot be targeted until end of round, as above. Passive reaction: At any time while this skill is active (including midway through an enemy Move) make a Ranged Attack and become Fatigued.",
        "tags": [
          "rogue",
          "profession"
        ],
        "source": {
          "name": "reference-rogue.pdf",
          "url": "imports/maladum-cards/reference-rogue.pdf"
        }
      },
