        "name": "Distraction",
        "type": "skill",
        "rulesText": "1. A character in medium range and LoS is Fatigued.\n2. Make a Ranged Attack/Throw. Target or other enemy in short range of target suffers 2 Fatigue in addition to other effects. Then Move.\n3. Choose character in medium range and LoS. Move them (may not engage or cause harm). They suffer 2 Fatigue. In any order, before or after moving target, you may Move and Attack.",
        "tags": [
          "rogue",
          "profession"
