        "rulesText": "1. Use when targeted with ranged attack or spell when within 4 squares of cover. Move into cover.\n2. Use when targeted with ranged attack or spell when within 4 squares of cover. Move into cover and ignore effects of attack.\n3. Use any time. In any order, Move into cover ignoring AoO and Attack. You cannot be targeted until end of round while still.",
